ter=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1106200/extras/5df5bfbd21824842f16b6ea0ac3b9cd7.poster.avif?t=1620549027\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1106200/extras/5df5bfbd21824842f16b6ea0ac3b9cd7.webm?t=1620549027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1106200/extras/5df5bfbd21824842f16b6ea0ac3b9cd7.mp4?t=1620549027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This episode is a simulator of a Russian gopnik (urban white trash) struggling through an identity crisis. Its unique mechanics allows you to think about the vanity of all worldly things while wandering around a bad neighbourhood.",
